{"tid":668734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉不良營商　健身中心6人被捕","createTime":"2018-05-18T01:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T07:16:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"99455b4bdeb682cc193db3fde61819065857cbac","tid":668734,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:16:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180518/20394467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F20394467&d=0lMTb%2Be1X1udiJY8OEQYvNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=10df8849\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180518%2F20394467&h=fd18ee1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180518/20394467</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月18日 <br />\n<br />\n涉不良營商　健身中心6人被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180518/large/aaaaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180518%2Flarge%2Faaaaa.jpg&h=0a53202a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉不良營商的健身中心職員落網。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】油麻地登打士街一間健身中心涉嫌以不良營商手法，施加不當影響，逼兩名16歲學生購買分別3,000元及1.8萬元健身會籍。海關經調查後，昨日再拘捕健身中心兩名職員，連同早前拘捕的另外兩名職員及兩名董事，至今共拘捕6人。<br />\n<br />\n海關版權及商標調查科高級貿易管制主任陳燕康指出，上月尾接獲兩受害學生投訴，指於旺角街頭被游說到健身中心免費試玩，其間被扣起身份證及提款卡，職員在未經他們同意之下，聲稱已過數購買會籍，分別為3,000元及1.8萬元。海關接報到場展開調查，於4月24日拘捕健身中心兩名職員及兩名董事（年齡由20歲至64歲）；至昨日再拘捕兩名職員（年齡20歲及24歲），被捕人士涉嫌使用具威嚇性的營業行為銷售服務，違反《商品說明條例》。<br />\n<br />\n■記者溫文學  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n又有紅van超載　59歲司機被捕<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n毆劫揸𨋢員&emsp; 賊匿朋友家落網"},{"pid":"ffd990a04788e1bd434df3f5ce659c3a4ad37541","tid":668734,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:19:34.000Z","msg":"邊間呢?"},{"pid":"ef4567fef8407492100b58c210e3e6e65e776fa7","tid":668734,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:20:18.000Z","msg":"登打士街有健身中心咩？"},{"pid":"d8289e5a5d04d5cde509d15420eeee715ff92380","tid":668734,"uid":5343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:36:40.000Z","msg":"Tf 執左應該冇啦wo"},{"pid":"2fa6643f456df0ce256548aebbe696d4e1968c51","tid":668734,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:50:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>登打士街有健身中心咩？</blockquote><br />\n可能係彌敦道與登打士街交界位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd24343e2da5a42592b95bd8d985702d5e595676","tid":668734,"uid":117837,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:03:36.000Z","msg":"睇錯 涉營養不良　健身中心6人被捕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559ee7f5fc8d420a9b978924af8a15e41936c14b","tid":668734,"uid":121473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:04:44.000Z","msg":"連學生都捉黎當水魚，唔係咁賤啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7927988526be1688c8269312486f5cec9681abb2","tid":668734,"uid":8392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:06:48.000Z","msg":"呢班仆街拉晒就啱"},{"pid":"89bfb0697689305cd4b1aa2df77f5a7116c4dbb7","tid":668734,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:07:38.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2659ec2fa527c6bf5fdbc9cc103f599a09e1b07b","tid":668734,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"559ee7f5fc8d420a9b978924af8a15e41936c14b","tid":668734,"uid":121473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"s